            <title>[DERBY-3695] NullPointerException when invoking statement event listeners if one of the listeners is null</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3695</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If PooledConnection.addStatementEventListener() is called with a null argument, the client driver throws a NullPointerException when the listeners are invoked. Embedded does not throw an exception.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
